{"tid":2180245,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Robert Pattinson 最喜愛15部電影","createTime":"2020-08-29T16:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T12:47:08.000Z","uid":157092,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"26d4694fc447b00f39745b7d33d480370f79ae23","tid":2180245,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:48:02.000Z","msg":"Source :<br />\n<a href=\"https://faroutmagazine.co.uk/robert-pattinson-15-favourite-films-list/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffaroutmagazine.co.uk%2Frobert-pattinson-15-favourite-films-list%2F&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLBF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=92dd6524\" target=\"_blank\">https://faroutmagazine.co.uk/robert-pattinson-15-favourite-films-list/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/130134927024045/posts/3165755313461976/?sfnsn=mo&amp;extid=moYn2nBdLZZbEl3Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F130134927024045%2Fposts%2F3165755313461976%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo%26extid%3DmoYn2nBdLZZbEl3Q&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLBF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=64bc9fd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/130134927024045/posts/3165755313461976/?sfnsn=mo&amp;extid=moYn2nBdLZZbEl3Q</a><br />\n<br />\n以下是Robert Pattinson的最愛15部電影：<br />\n1. One Flew Over the Cuckoo&rsquo;s Nest《飛越杜鵑窩》 &ndash; Milo&scaron; Forman, 1975.<br />\n2. Breathless《斷了氣》 &ndash; Jean-Luc Godard, 1960.<br />\n3. The Exorcist《大法師》 &ndash; William Friedkin, 1973.<br />\n4. Julia &ndash; Erick Zonca, 2008.<br />\n5. Headhunters《獵頭遊戲》 &ndash; Morten Tyldum, 2012.<br />\n6. The Devils《群魔》 &ndash; Ken Russell, 1971.<br />\n7. The Beat That My Heart Skipped《我心遺忘的節奏》 &ndash; Jacques Audiard, 2005.<br />\n8. Arizona Dream《亞歷桑那夢遊》 &ndash; Emir Kusturica, 1993.<br />\n9. Pierrot le Fou《狂人皮埃羅》 &ndash; Jean-Luc Godard, 1965.<br />\n10. Ivans Xtc &ndash; Bernard Rose, 2002.<br />\n11. First Name: Carmen《芳名卡門》 &ndash; Jean-Luc Godard, 1983.<br />\n12. Deep Breath《深呼吸》 &ndash; Damien Odoul, 2001.<br />\n13. Corky Romano《聯邦大蠢探》 &ndash; Rob Pritts, 2001.<br />\n14. White Material《白鬼子》 &ndash; Claire Denis, 2009.<br />\n15. The Lovers on the Bridge《新橋戀人》 &ndash; Leos Carax, 1991.<br />\n<br />\nJean-Luc Godard（尚盧&middot;高達）就佔了15部中的3部，且幾乎沒有商業電影，尤其喜歡《新橋戀人》 更是令人大心！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌，冇一套睇過"},{"pid":"f533c052001723a9f7e4456d964ba27f5e4159a4","tid":2180245,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494cf2495c40619b59338a994fbcd6a63a775de8","tid":2180245,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b58b5c7b579ffbca47c93701ad6229d3d7a661f","tid":2180245,"uid":18012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"1套都未睇過+1"},{"pid":"17ca50e5a6f53073a1eed95d219ea4e37d89ba64","tid":2180245,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b58b5c7b579ffbca47c93701ad6229d3d7a661f","tid":2180245,"uid":18012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"1套都未睇過+1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過taste 相當優質"},{"pid":"a248174f2bf314aeae15d419a9b472d760900e80","tid":2180245,"uid":134521,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"《飛越杜鵑窩》香港人必睇 完全係講緊香港現況"},{"pid":"7cb6ed3cad4cb25f8f89f1489e7cc3e8280040ac","tid":2180245,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29